lyrics:
[Verse]
In the heart of the Andes, majestic mountains stand
La Cordillera de los Andes, unites this sacred land
Machu Picchu's ancient ruins, a testament of time
Where Aymara culture thrives, their spirit so sublime

[Chorus]
Oh, la Cordillera de los Andes, where dreams take flight
Machu Picchu shines, in the morning's golden light
Aymara heritage, strong and proud, it will never fade
As the condor soars above, an emblem of their grace
